lead_paragraph: Stephan Jaeger broke one more Web.com Tour record and tied another Sunday in the Ellie Mae Classic, finishing his four-day scoring frenzy at TPC Stonebrae at 30-under 250.

headline.print_headline: Stephan Jaeger Finishes Off Record Web.com Tour Romp
